## 步骤 8：推送 + PR

1. 带上游跟踪推送：
   ```bash
   git push -u origin HEAD
   ```

2. **PR 幂等性检查** — 创建新 PR 前检测已有 PR：
   ```bash
   EXISTING_PR=$(gh pr view --json url,number,state -q 'select(.state == "OPEN") | .number' 2>/dev/null || echo "")
   ```
   - 如果 `EXISTING_PR` 非空：使用 `gh pr edit $EXISTING_PR --body "..."` 更新已有 PR body
   - 如果为空：创建新 PR

3. 创建或更新 PR：
   ```bash
   gh pr create --base {{ trunk_branch }} --title "<type>: <summary>" --body "$(cat <<'EOF'
   ## Summary
   <总结所有变更 — 按逻辑部分分组>

   ## Evaluation Scores
   | Dimension | Score |
   |-----------|-------|
   | Design | architect | X/10 |
   | Completeness | product-owner | X/10 |
   | Quality | engineer | X/10 |
   | Regression | qa | X/10 |
   | Scope | project-manager | X/10 |
   | **Weighted Average** | | **X.X/10** |

   ## Review Findings
   - High confidence: N findings
   - Auto-fixed: M findings
   - Roles dispatched: architect ✓/✗  product-owner ✓/✗  engineer ✓/✗  qa ✓/✗  project-manager ✓/✗

   ## Plan Completion
   <完成度清单摘要，或 "No plan file">

   ## Scope Check
   <CLEAN 或列出漂移/缺失项>

   ## Test Coverage
   <ASCII 覆盖率图摘要，或 "No coverage audit">

   ## TODOS
   <N completed, M remaining, 或 "No TODOS.md">

   ## Test Results
   - [x] All tests pass (N tests)

   EOF
   )"
   ```

   如果 `gh` 不可用：打印分支名和远程 URL 以供手动创建 PR。

4. 输出 PR URL。

